==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Platonize
<hw>Pla"to*nize</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To explain by, or accomodate
to, the Platonic philosophy.</def> <rj><au>Enfield.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Platonizer</ent>⟦br⟧
